criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

  -  Patients undergoing orthognathic surgery during the study and with surgical
     technique:

       -  sagittal maxillary bilateral osteotomy;

       -  maxillary;

       -  vertical osteotomy;

       -  Lefort I osteotomy combined with or without mentoplastia and maxillary
          disjunction.

  -  Informed consent

  -  Patients in the maxillofacial outpatient clinic located at Sao Paulo

Exclusion Criteria:

  -  patients undergoing reoperation of orthognathic surgery;

  -  with cleft lip-palate.
